desc.p:
When there is no pending connection to return, the function will return {select, SelectInfo}, and the caller will later receive a select message, {'$socket', Socket, select, SelectHandle} ( with the SelectHandle contained in the
SelectInfo
) when a client connects. A subsequent call to accept/1,2 will then return the socket.

item.p:
It is common that for the protocol domain local
it is mandatory to not select a protocol, that is;
to select the default protocol.
